  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Smile a child. Renovate the Clinic in Poland</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project is run by the Association for Development of Child Surgery based in Wroclaw, Poland.  The building that currently houses the Children Clinic is in a very bad condition (i.e. the roof is leaking). Moreover the interiors and clinic furniture are in a deplorable state. The clinic is not properly adjusted to host babies. The Association is urgently looking for funds to renovate the building and by doing so, improving the conditions of hospitalized little patients and their guardians.</narrative>
  </description>
